data.title: Chicago Public Schools
data.meta_description: Chicago Public Schools is committed to providing a high-quality education to all students, and preparing them for success in college, career, and civic life.
data.text:
09 August 2024

Sign Up at 10 a.m. Today to Attend Our Next Public Negotiation Session

In a letter to families, CPS provides a reminder to sign up to attend the next public bargaining session.

08 August 2024

Preparing for our Next Public Negotiation Session

In a letter to families, CPS CEO Pedro Martinez provides details about the upcoming public negotiation session.

06 August 2024

Important Health Reminders for the New School Year

In a letter to families, CPS provides an update on important health reminders for the new school year.

31 July 2024

An Update on Contract Negotiations between CPS and the CTU

In a letter to families, CPS CEO Pedro Martinez recaps the District's latest public negotiation session.
